Updates an existing flow

Source: R/appflow_operations.R
appflow_update_flow.Rd

Updates an existing flow.

appflow_update_flow(flowName, description, triggerConfig,
  sourceFlowConfig, destinationFlowConfigList, tasks)

Arguments

flowName

[required] The specified name of the flow. Spaces are not allowed. Use underscores (\_) or hyphens (-) only.
description

A description of the flow.
triggerConfig

[required] The trigger settings that determine how and when the flow runs.
sourceFlowConfig
destinationFlowConfigList

[required] The configuration that controls how Amazon AppFlow transfers data to the destination connector.
tasks

[required] A list of tasks that Amazon AppFlow performs while transferring the data in the flow run.
